description: At last! The long awaited sequel to last year's surprise hit, the sold-out LAST HERO STANDING, which Ray Tate of Silver Bullet Comics called 'a comic book mini-series that's worth buying!' For centuries beyond reckoning, Galactus has consumed entire worlds to satiate his never-ending quest for sustenance, but now he has a new plan--one which may threaten the very existence of the entire Universe! Featuring: the mighty Thor, the Warriors Three, the Avengers, Spider-Girl, the Fantastic Five and the Shi'ar Imperial Guard!

The sequel to the critically acclaimed LAST HERO STANDING continues--! A major Marvel Universe character dies! The Great Elders and Cosmic Powers of the Universe launch a desperate attack against Galactus! The citizens of Earth are ordered to evacuate the planet! New York City is targeted for destruction! The Silver Surfer joins the fray! And, the action hits overdrive as the Avengers, Spider-Girl and the Fantastic Five prepare to make their final stand!

The sequel to the critically acclaimed LAST HERO STANDING continues--! A major Marvel Universe character dies! The Great Elders and Comic Powers of the Universe launch a desperate attack against Galactus! The citizens of Earth are ordered to evacuate the planet! New York City is targeted for destruction! The Silver Surfer joins the fray! And the action hits overdrive as the Avengers, Spider-Girl and the Fantastic Five prepare to make their final stand!

Is this the end of the MC-2 Universe? The sequel to last year's surprise hit concludes and it's all-out action in the merry Marvel manner as...Determined to evolve, Galactus prepares to sacrifice the Earth and the entire universe! An army of Mainframes take on a horde of Punisher robots! The Silver Surfer unleashes his full cosmic fury against his former master! The last heroes standing make their final assault on the planet-eater! And Spider-Girl and a few friends take a desperate, perhaps fatal, gamble to save their world and the universe entire!

They called him a fool… a madman… a blasphemer who threatened the very laws of nature. But within the wreckage of a fallen spaceship, Vicktor Luthor found the key to creating life anew. Now, Luthor's lab-created Superman, possessed of powers far beyond those of mortal men, threatens to destroy not only his creator, but all those who come in contact with him.
name: The Superman Monster

description: Five brutal stories exploring how the changes wrought by DARK REIGN have affected the criminal community throughout the Marvel Universe! Spymaster takes on a hazardous assignment for Norman Osborn! Attuma is resurrected by Doctor Doom! A new Jack O'Lantern confronts the police! Gamma Corps confronts the Iron Patriot! And the new Enforcer marks his territory with the Hood!
name: Made Men

description: After an incompetent archaeologist wagers away the last of his capital, a surprising (and, sadly, apparently unparalleled) night of passion sets him on a voyage outside his wildest dreams. Soon he is caught in a possibly lethal web of conspiracy, for the ancient riches and mysteries he exposes are sought-after by evil forces both worldly and paranormal. But he finds that the dangers pale in contrast to the rewards he obtains, erotic pleasures so fantastic that only the Gods themselves can confer them!
name: Hathor

description: In desperate need for money, Conrad tries to fool the mysterious Dr. Branko but is not successful. And he still cannot forget his magic journeys into lust and ecstasy, meeting the old Egyptian goddesses one by one. He succumbs again and chooses Seschat, the fifth daughter of Isis. Her specialty: she can change into characters every man would like to have sex with. Conrad's pop-culture-fed mind goes into overdrive! More great, lusciously drawn, supernatural sex from Germany, from the producers of the Eros hit Alraune!
name: Seshat

description: Registered mutant 2099, Chad Channing, is a mild-mannered high school student at Baxter High. He takes his mutant gene suppression pills every morning and his parents couldn't be more proud of him. With the mutant threat neutralized the world is a safer place, crime is down, a Sentinel is on every corner, and life is pretty much perfect. But all that changes when Chad finds a secret basement located under the Baxter Building that houses the living brain of rebel leader Reed Richards.
name: Mutant 2099

description: After the mutant registration act being reinstated spurred a battle between mutants, super heroes, and the government, it was clear to the Inhumans that anything more than human... was not welcome on Earth. So they left for a life amongst the stars, but after an over-fifty- year journey they have arrived at their destination... but where could they be?
name: Inhumans 2099

description: Purveyor of perky perversion Rebecca, best known for her steamy Sapphic suburban scenes in her monster-hit titles Housewives at Play, Teens at Play, and Hot Moms, launches her luscious lesbian ladies into a new frontier of fantasy, fetish and frolic – outer space! Rebecca rolls out a rocket-powered ration of roving reprobates on the red planet. Zero gravity looks good on this batch of mature, Mars-dwelling, mammary mamas! Lushly rendered in pencils, life for the experienced spacewoman in the place where no man has gone before is detailed with a light, lustful touch. These seasoned, sexy space cadets will get your rocket firing as they keep each other company on their interplanetary journey, encountering ray-guns, robots, and wild alien life forms. Make sure your oxygen tanks are full because Rebecca will take your breath away with this out-of-this-world collection! 48-page softcover.
name: MILFS On Mars

description: T'Challa is gone, but Wakanda stands strong. The vibranium mines are still active and it remains one of the richest countries in the world. T'Challa left no heir, and since his passing a succession of Wakandans have attempted to claim the throne. Doctor Doom of Latveria has turned his sights on Wakanda; an invasion is imminent. But where is the Black Panther?
name: Black Panther 2099

description: The hot moms are at it again in Rebecca's sizzling FULL-COLOR comic book series. Desperate Housewives this is not. More like lustful, insatiable, and wanting housewives that give a new definition to your average MILF. After this you will never look at a 38-year old mother of three the same again. Suburban moms with the sexual experience you need and want, the charm and beauty you deserve, and the hunger and lust you desire. All this and in FULL-COLOR too!
name: The Dutiful Wife

description: Can YOU keep a secret? A hot summer day by the pool, a naughty teenage neighbor in a teeny tiny bikini, a HOT MOM with a preoccupied hubby, and a messy tube of suntan oil... what do YOU think is going to happen? And happen again? And again? Hidden desires bubble to the surface as Rebecca scorches the page with this ode to summertime suburban Sapphic sexuality! This special issue is drawn in the super lush pencil style of Rebecca's beloved and best-selling illustration collections. 24-page comic book.

Two college girls spend the morning innocently washing a car. Little do they know they're being "observed" by a horny neighbor. Of course, the neighbor is a woman old enough to be one of their moms, and they decide to have a little fun by helping her to give in to her fantasies. It's another kinky full-color fantasy by Housewives at Play's naughty Rebecca!
name: Teen Angel

description: A young girl named Jenna is desperate to escape an abusive relationship before it's too late, and a chance meeting with Sela might just provide her a way out. But when Jenna finds happiness in another man's arms, the abusive Drew is not about to let the couple live happily ever after! When a young man is transformed into a hideous beast, he is granted a short time to change his ways. But will the beast learn from his mistakes, or will he continue down a path of destruction? Don't miss the unbelievable collected edition of Beauty and the Beast that includes an ending that will blow readers away!
name: Beauty & The Beast
